Project details

I successfully migrated a WooCommerce store to Shopify, enhancing functionality and user experience. Here's a brief overview of the process:

Backup & Preparation:
Created a full backup of the WordPress site.
Set up a subdomain for testing to ensure a smooth transition.

Shopify Setup:
Created a Shopify account and customized a template to match the original stores design and functionality.

Data Migration:
Imported products, customers, and orders from WooCommerce to Shopify using CSV files, ensuring accuracy in all data.

Integrations & Customizations:
Email Marketing: Integrated tools for customer engagement and automated review requests.
Facebook Pixel: Implemented for enhanced ad targeting and performance tracking.
Custom Checkout: Developed a streamlined checkout process to improve user experience.
Shipping Rates: Configured accurate shipping rates and zones.
Payment Gateway: Integrated secure payment options.

Testing & Launch
Conducted testing to ensure all features function correctly and optimized for mobile and desktop.
Launched the Shopify store with minimal downtime and provided training for ongoing management.

Custom WordPress Website Development: From scratch to an advanced stage, I can build a system that attracts a steady flow of dream customers to take your business.

WordPress Theme Customization: I can customize any WordPress theme you need including WordPress Avada Theme, WordPress Ultra Theme, WordPress Thrive Theme, WordPress Flat-Some Theme, and WordPress Elegant Diva Theme.

WooCommerce Development: Whether you need an E-commerce website or need WooCommerce customization, I can help you.

SEO-Friendly Website Development: I am an On-Page SEO Expert, Off-Page SEO, and can conduct an SEO Audit, and SEO Keywords Research to optimize your website for search engines.

PSD and Figma Design Into HTML/WP: I can convert PSD and Figma design into HTML and WordPress websites.

WordPress Themes & Plugins Installations: I am familiar with all popular WordPress plugins including WPML, WP Rocket, WordPress Yoast SEO, WordPress Organic Rank Math SEO Expert, Elementor Pro, Divi Builder, WP-Bakery.

Google Cloud Platform (GCP) Expert: I can migrate your website, Application to Google Cloud Platform (GCP), Install Lamp Stack, Ubuntu, Centos07, and WordPress, and Create VMs to reduce your cost of hosting.

Database Optimization: I can develop any type of Database (SQL SERVER, MYSQL) and optimize it to increase the speed of queries and data using audit, MVP, and SP.

Digital Marketing Integration: I will set up and integrate Google Analytics, Google Tag Manager, and Facebook Pixel with your platform to track what our customer is doing by tracking button clicks, outbound links, form submission, scroll depth, setting and tracking funnels, checkout behavior, shopping behavior, and transactions.
